(60, 1, '2018-10-10 12:09:15', '2018-10-10 12:09:15', 'The human civilization seems to have reached the epitome of technological advancement. Yet, various attempts are made to achieve more and move ahead in technological terms. Newer devices embedded with more advanced technologies are innovated and manufacturer every now and then. More than half of the human population is directly or indirectly connected to each other via uncountable social media platforms, telecommunication devices and the greatest of all – Internet.\r\n\r\nInternet and technologies related to it has been so revolutionary and impactful in human lives that it is extremely difficult to imagine a future without it. Children born in the 21<sup>st</sup> century seem to be highly skilled in using technology right from their childhood. People in general, irrespective of their age, are up to some extent dependent on technology in some way or the other. Starting from small household chores or everyday jobs to life turning decisions, most of these things are dependent on technological interventions.\r\n\r\nReviewtech.in brings you all the relevant news, developments and major events in the technology sector. The reviews done by our team caters to the needs of both, the consumers and the business owners as it deals with both the parties.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-10 12:09:15', '2018-10-10 12:09:15', '', 31, 'http://localhost/techreview/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
