(123, 1, '2018-10-12 07:13:46', '2018-10-12 07:13:46', 'They say, ‘Home is the heart is’. It is the place people feel the safest and happiest. It is the place where one can meet his/her family, eat and drink together, live a prosperous life. Gadgets have always made our lives better in numerous ways. They have allowed us to spend quality time with our family in the comfort of our living rooms. Appliances such as Air Conditioners, Washing machines, Televisions, Refrigerators, Microwaves and so on add to the comfort level. Tradition technology in electronics was good enough but introducing smart features in these appliances have added to the value. Users are able to control the smart appliances with the help of their smartphones. Most of the smart appliances can even be controlled with the users’ voices. This is possible due to the voice recognition software.', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '123', '', '', '2018-10-12 07:43:55', '2018-10-12 07:43:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/techreview/?p=123', 4, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
