(5, 5, 'category', 'They say, ‘Home is the heart is’. It is the place people feel the safest and happiest. It is the place where one can meet his/her family, eat and drink together, live a prosperous life. Gadgets have always made our lives better in numerous ways. They have allowed us to spend quality time with our family in the comfort of our living rooms. Appliances such as Air Conditioners, Washing machines, Televisions, Refrigerators, Microwaves and so on add to the comfort level.\r\nTradition technology in electronics was good enough but introducing smart features in these appliances have added to the value. Users are able to control the smart appliances with the help of their smartphones. Most of the smart appliances can even be controlled with the users’ voices. This is possible due to the voice recognition software. ', 0, 2),
(6, 6, 'category', ' Internet has emerged as the power that has enabled the common person to do unimaginable things. The power has not changed its structure much but the things that can be done with the help of internet is beyond imagination. Earlier, computer were necessary to use internet but since the invention of smartphones, internet can be accessed from anywhere with a good network reception quality. ', 0, 1),
(7, 7, 'category', '', 0, 0),
(8, 8, 'category', 'Artificial intelligence or AI is demonstrated by machines, in contrast to the natural intelligence displayed by humans and other animals. In computer science, AI research is defined as the study of \"intelligent agents\": any device that perceives its environment and takes actions that maximize its chance of successfully achieving its goals. Colloquially, the term \"artificial intelligence\" is applied when a machine mimics \"cognitive\" functions that humans associate with other human minds, such as \"learning\" and \"problem solving\r\nAI has a very wide scope in today’s technology and is quickly seeping into our daily lives. Smartphones and Laptops are coming equipped with AI enabled chipsets and camera modules. Most of the major technology giants have developed their own AI voice assistants, which help the users in getting their things done with just a voice command. These technological advancements are helping the users to get a more customized experience.', 0, 2),
(9, 9, 'category', 'Smartphone and internet penetration has witnessed a stellar rise in India. This has led to an exponential growth in the e-commerce and mobile commerce or (m-commerce) sector in the country. The sector is looking healthy and is moving forward with greater chances of commendable growth in the next couple of years. It is the perfect time to invest in online businesses or start one.\r\nIn order to be a successful e-retailer, a perfectly streamlined website is imperative. There are various service providers that help the new businesses get their web needs fulfilled right from scratch without you having to deal with any technicalities. These facilities have made starting an e-commerce business easier than ever before.\r\nThe global giants are joining hands with the local major players in an attempt the capture the huge market that India is offering. Competition is extremely high in this sector and companies are on each other’s throat to lead the market. Loyalty programmed, massive discounts, sales and various offers are given to lure the customers all year round. The huge e-commerce platforms have taken the consumers away from the offline stores and this has irked all the small offline players. We look closely into the practical details of the e-commerce sector and analyse the impacts of each one of them.', 0, 2),
